Japan’s Fukushima Plant Had Problems Before Earthquake, WSJ Says

-- B y   M i k e   M i l l a r d
-- 
2011-03-21T03:04:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/japan-s-fukushima-plant-had-problems-before-earthquake-wsj-says.html
  Japan ’s Fukushima Daiichi power
plant was a troubled facility before the earthquake and tsunami
damaged its cooling systems and caused a nuclear crisis, the
Wall Street Journal reported, citing its analysis of regulatory
documents.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
